title: How long are queue times in silver+ elos?

replies.body: It really depends on the time of day.
Silver 2, 2:30 but sometimes if you're lucky u get under 1 min queues. I just got one in 22 seconds...

Best times to get into queue:

Bronze - 3:00pm - 10:00pm
Silver - 12:30pm - 10:00pm
Gold - 12:30pm - 10:00pm

I don't really know the other ranks, cause I play around these elos.
Plus I was Bronze 5, so ;-;
I'M SILVER 4 GO EZ ON ME
in plat during peak times its around 2 minutes
